dct_title_s: A plan of Paris &c. This survey has been reduced to the same scale as that of London & the country around it survey'd and publish'd in 16 sheets = Plan de Paris &c. Ce plan a été reduit sur la meme eschelle de celui de Londres et de ses environs en 16 feuilles
dct_description_sm: Facsimile. Relief shown by hachures. "... an edition limited to 500 copies." "Reproduced in 1970 by Historic Urban Plans ... from an engraving in its collection." Historic Maps copy is no. 12.
